"On tap for ""Sour Night"" at The Brew Kettle in Strongsville, Ohio during Cleveland Beer Week 2014.  My first gose, so I wasn't sure what to expect.  It reminded me of a Berliner Weisse in terms of tartness, but with the wheat character and chewiness of a wit beer or light wheat beer thrown in.  Very light, clean and refreshing."
