"Aroma was heavy on the coriander, taste was similar, with an herbal bitterness and tea-like impression due to the heavy handed coriander addition. Also hot dogs. Tart lemon, lactobacillus. This wasn't very drinkable to me. Gose is something you can quaff liters of, and this ain't that."
